name: Frisbee 3D
description:
Tap to throw the frisbee to the next player.

Aim the frisbee taking into account the wind speed and direction.

If you did not aim perfectly, you can move the next player around so he/she catches the frisbee. Drag the finger to move.

Try to achieve the final hoop to advance to the next level.

Increasing level of difficulty!

Can you get to level 100?
